title: Rep. Hollingsworth, 2020 Election Delay

description:
Guests: Mario Parker, Bloomberg White House reporter, Matt Bennett, Co-Founder Third Way and Democratic Strategist, Alex Vogel, CEO of the Vogel Group, and former Chief Counsel for Senate Majority Leader Bill Frist, Congressman Trey Hollingsworth, a Republican representing Indiana's 9th district.
